TestDressify/
│
├── app.py                      # Main entry point (the merged app.py)
├── extensions.py               # Database and Bcrypt initialization
├── .env                        # Your SECRET_KEY, CLIENT_ID, and DATABASE_URL
├── flask_session/              # Created automatically (stores Snap OAuth sessions)
│
├── routes/                     # Blueprint folders
│   ├── auth_routes.py
│   ├── avatar_routes.py        # ⬅️ Snap OAuth routes go here
│   ├── ai_routes.py
│   └── product_routes.py
│
├── static/                     # CSS, JS, and Images
│   ├── css/
│   │   └── indexstyle.css      # Your main stylesheet
│   └── js/
│       └── navbar-init.js
│
├── templates/                  # ⬅️ ALL HTML files must be here
│   ├── index.html
│   └── avatar-customizer.html  # Your main customization page
│
└── uploads/                    # Stores user-uploaded style references